{
  "stem": "2830.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what he did is spoke a-- a very fine, you know, intelligentsia, is what you would call that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Cause he said his own verse on that and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came, and I risked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You risked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know what a date is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we walked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he started talking about, you know, somewhere we were from, when and everything he told me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he spoke, I-- I knew that he knew a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very intelligent, and very-- you know-- I liked, you know, what he said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't thought anything about it, I mean, you know, that was not even in my mind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Polish language he used was intelligentsia, you know, educated boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that I'm the maven, but I knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in the meantime, I had somebody else who was really interested in me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a dentist in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came from-- he was from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He kind of got away from Poland, everybody winds up in Bergen-Belsen because that was the women's-- you know-- Camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Camp, liberated, so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he stayed in the-- in the same block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was a nice-- the SS used to live there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this man tried to come on to me, and he was much older than I am.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a dentist, you know-- then, so I figure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew he was coming on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to go and-- and-- bring-- nobody-- I don't know where he got flowers-- bring flowers, all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he used to take walks with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took walks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was serious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He started to be serious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he told me--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
